<GuideLayout
  title="Utilities Setup Gulf 2026 | DEWA, Kahramaa & SEC Guide"
  description="Register DEWA (Dubai), ADDC (Abu Dhabi), Kahramaa (Qatar) or SEC (Saudi) in 24-48 hours. Deposits, monthly costs from AED 300 (~€75), internet setup and documents."
